flowchart TB
    A[Two patients' data<br/>x and y] --> B[Encode each into<br/>a quantum circuit]
    B --> C[Run circuit that<br/>compares them]
    C --> D[Measure: chance of<br/>all-zeros = similarity]
    D --> E[Similarity number<br/>goes into a table]
    E --> F[Normal classifier SVM<br/>uses the table to decide]
    F --> G{Sick or not?}
    style B fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#4527A0
    style C fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#4527A0
    style F fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32
